export const style = {
  position: "absolute",
  top: "50%",
  left: "50%",
  transform: "translate(-50%, -50%)",
  width: 400,
  height: 200,
  bgcolor: "background.paper",
  border: "2px solid #000",
  boxShadow: 24,
  p: 10,
};

export const style2 = {
  maxWidth: 445,
  padding: 3,
  position: "relative",
  top: "30%",
  left: "38%",
  boxShadow: "216, 210, 210, 0.842",
  borderRadius: "10px",
};
